fields.name: Authorities have processes in place for outsiders
Has level & dry area of land (200-400m2)
Semi-level access from road to house
Semi-level level for majority of property
Visual privacy from neighbours (5 = non visible)
Not overlooked (? same as visual privacy ?)
Protected from the elements (i.e. not exposed to wind/rain)
Nearby population centre (ideally within 15 minute walk)
Land has interesting terrain or features
Has water that could be a feature (high spring, unobtrusive river, high well)
Future infrastructure projects planned for area
Possibility to purchase neighbouring plots in future
